    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《魔力构造》是一款<strong>自由编辑技能</strong>的动作生存类游戏。利用<strong>简单的连接机制</strong>，自由组合技能模块，构筑属于你的专属技能，<strong><u>单人挑战</u></strong>，或<strong><u>2-4人组队冒险</u></strong>，在充满挑战的世界中生存并变强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供多种<strong>难度tag选择</strong>，定制专属你的游戏体验。而全新加入的<strong>【无尽模式】</strong>将带来截然不同的玩法——永远充满未知与惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你，准备好迎接这场魔法与生存的终极挑战了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >临危不乱的战斗体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爽快附带异常状态的攻击</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种各样的神奇怪物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>技能系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过连接新的插件，使投射物获得此插件的属性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连接的插件越多，投射物也就越强</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分插件的属性可以调节</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>难度系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地图都提供了多种多样的标签</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种标签对应一种机制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过选择各个标签实现不一样的游戏体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/1b184be4e68cce2a158ff8bef87fbd15.avif?t=1752520599\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras_big/1b184be4e68cce2a158ff8bef87fbd15.avif?t=1752520599 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成就系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁成就可获得新的道具、角色、属性等内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/8957d3c9e18f311cd69c531fa0caee95.avif?t=1752520599\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras_big/8957d3c9e18f311cd69c531fa0caee95.avif?t=1752520599 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于我们</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《魔力构造》是由2人小团队用爱发电制作的。我们大约每两周发布一次更新（详看游戏里的“更新日志”），会持续优化游戏体验。<br>每一位玩家的反馈对我们都至关重要，我们会认真阅读每一条评价和建议，并尽力在后续版本中改进。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多语言支持</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏现支持12种语言，非中文版本目前采用AI翻译+人工校对的方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于语言差异，翻译可能存在不完美的地方，如果您发现任何问题，欢迎通过Steam社区或直接联系我们反馈，我们会尽快修正！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
